 graduate in  nomikos cofounded with hatsopoulos the thermo electron corporation thermo electron became a major provider of analytical instruments and services for a variety of domains under the development of george hatsopoulos john hatsopoulos and arvin smith in  george hatsopoulos was president of the thermo electron engineering corporation and senior lecturer in mechanical engineering at mitin  hatsopoulos won the john fritz medal which is the highest american award in the engineering profession and presented each year for scientific or industrial achievement in any field of pure or applied science in  he was awarded the rd annual heinz award in technology the economy and employment mr hatsopoulos is also a recipient of the international center in new yorks award of excellence in  along with arvin smith and john hatsopoulos he was awarded the  pittcon heritage award from the chemical heritage foundationsee alsohistory of thermodynamicsreferences  a b mit  appointments to administrative positions and four faculty changes announced the tech lxxvi no   httptechmiteduvpdfnpdf hatsopoulos george n keenan joseph h  principles of general thermodynamics john wiley  sons inc ccn   cs maint multiple names authors list link gyftopoulos elias p beretta gian paolo  thermodynamics foundations and applications dover pu inc isbn   see eg httpwwwquantumthermodynamicsorg hatsopoulos george nicholas  the thermoelectron engine doctoral dissertation massachusetts institute of technology cambridge massachusetts usa httphdlhandlenet it dont mean a thing if you aint got that green hbs and the birth of venture capital hbs bulletin online december  httpwwwalumnihbsedubulletindecemberstarthtml george and john hatsopoulos and arvin smith chemical heritage foundation archived from the original on july   retrieved  june   the heinz awards george hatsopoulos profileexternal linksgeorge hatsopoulos  biographygeorge hatsopoulos  national academy of engineering chairman and ceo text is available