ing a term as chairman since  he has been a director of ilios inc he has been a director of cyberkinetics neurotechnology systems inc since august  he served as a director of tecogen inc since  until june   dr hatsopoulos served as a director of thermedics inc since  he served as a director of american dg energy inc from july  to may   he served as a director of thermo electron corporation since  thermo instrument systems inc since  thermo ecotek corporation since  thermoquest corporation since june  thermotrex corporation since  and thermo optek corporation since august  he served as a director of photoelectron corp and thermo fibertek inc he served as a member of the boards of various corporations and institutions he is a life member of the corporation of mit he was a faculty member of mit from  to  he was a senior lecturer at massachusetts institute of technology until  he has authored over  articles in professional journals and is the principal author of textbooks in thermodynamics and thermionic energy conversion he is the recipient of numerous honors and awards in engineering science industry and academics dr hatsopoulos is a fellow of the american academy of arts and sciences the american society of mechanical engineers and other scientific and technical organizations dr hatsopoulos holds a bachelors degree from the national technical university of athens in  and his masters degree in  his bachelorsengineers degree in  and his doctorate degree in  from mit – all in mechanical engineeringread full background corporate headquarters  st avenuewaltham massachusetts united statesphone fax  board members memberships there is no board members memberships data available education doctorate massachusetts institute of technologybachelors degree massachusetts institute of technologymasters degree massachusetts institute of technologybachelors degree national technical university of athens other affiliations thermotrex corporationthermedics incthermo instrument systems i