y statements of the second law and has provided a basis to extend the traditional definition of entropy to the nonequilibrium domain in  hatsopoulos also contributed to a formulation of a unified theory of mechanics and thermodynamics arguably a precursor of the emerging field of quantum thermodynamics overviewedit while at mit hatsopoulos was head of the engineering division of matrad corporation new york matrad corporation and mit financially supported his doctoral thesis the thermoelectron engine matrad corporation was owned by the family of peter m nomikos a harvard business school graduate in  nomikos cofounded with hatsopoulos the thermo electron corporation thermo electron became a major provider of analytical instruments and services for a variety of domains under the development of george hatsopoulos john hatsopoulos and arvin smith in  george hatsopoulos was president of the thermo electron engineering corporation and senior lecturer in mechanical engineering at mit in  hatsopoulos won the john fritz medal which is the highest american award in the engineering profession and presented each year for scientific or industrial achievement in any field of pure or applied science in  he was awarded the rd annual heinz award in technology the economy and employment mr hatsopoulos is also a recipient of the international center in new yorks award of excellence in  along with arvin smith and john hatsopoulos he was awarded the  pittcon heritage award from the chemical heritage foundation see alsoedit history of thermodynamics referencesedit    a b mit  appointments to administrative positions and four faculty changes announced the tech lxxvi no   httptechmiteduvpdfnpdf  hatsopoulos george n keenan joseph h  principles of general thermodynamics john wiley  sons inc ccn  cs maint multiple names authors list link  gyftopoulos elias p beretta gian paolo  thermodynamics foundations and applications dover pu inc isbn    see eg httpwwwquantumthermodynamicsorg  hatsopoulos